## Mocking and Stubbing

### Stubbing Methods

```ruby
test "external API call" do
  # Stub method to return specific value
  ArticleAPI.stub :fetch, { title: "Test" } do
    article = Article.import_from_api
    assert_equal "Test", article.title
  end
end
```

### Mocking Time

```ruby
test "article publishes at scheduled time" do
  future_time = 1.day.from_now
  
  travel_to future_time do
    article = articles(:scheduled)
    assert article.published?
  end
end
```

